rop/Category" href="./Category:Articles_with_short_description" about="#mwt1" id="mwAw"/>
<p id="mwBA"><span typeof="mw:Nowiki mw:Transclusion" about="#mwt2" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Use dmy dates","href":"./Template:Use_dmy_dates"},"params":{"date":{"wt":"January 2019"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBQ"></span><link rel="mw:PageProp/Category" href="./Category:Use_dmy_dates_from_January_2019" about="#mwt2" id="mwBg"/></p>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt3" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Redirect2","href":"./Template:Redirect2"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Tolstoy"},"2":{"wt":"Tolstoi"},"3":{"wt":"other uses"},"4":{"wt":"Tolstoy (disambiguation)"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwBw">"Tolstoy" and "Tolstoi" redirect here. For other uses, see <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Tolstoy_(disambiguation)" title="Tolstoy (disambiguation)">Tolstoy (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt4" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Redirect","href":"./Template:Redirect"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Lev Tolstoy"},"2":{"wt":"the rural locality and the railway station in Lipetsk Oblast, Russia"},"3":{"wt":"Lev Tolstoy (rural locality)"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCA">"Lev Tolstoy" redirects here. For the rural locality and the railway station in Lipetsk Oblast, Russia, see <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Lev_Tolstoy_(rural_locality)" title="Lev Tolstoy (rural locality)">Lev Tolstoy (rural locality)</a>.</div>
<div role="note" class="hatnote navigation-not-searchable" about="#mwt5" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Eastern Slavic name","href":"./Template:Eastern_Slavic_name"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"Nikolayevich"},"2":{"wt":"Tolstoy"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwCQ">This name uses <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Eastern_Slavic_naming_customs" title="Eastern Slavic naming customs">Eastern Slavic naming customs</a>; the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Patronymic" title="Patronymic">patronymic</a> is <i>Nikolayevich</i><span typeof="mw:Entity"> </span>and the <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Surname" title="Surname">family name</a> is <i>Tolstoy</i>.</div>
