<li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Synthesis_anarchism" title="Synthesis anarchism">Synthesis anarchism</a></li></ul></td>
</tr><tr><th style="padding:0.1em;background-color:#f0f0f0">
<a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Libertarian_Marxism" title="Libertarian Marxism">Libertarian Marxist</a> tendencies</th></tr><tr><td class="plainlist" style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em">
<ul><li><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Autonomism" title="Autonomism">Autonomism</a></li>
