<div class="reflist " style=" list-style-type: decimal;" about="#mwt293" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"reflist","href":"./Template:Reflist"},"params":{"group":{"wt":"note"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAfY">
<div class="mw-references-wrap" typeof="mw:Extension/references" about="#mwt570" data-mw='{"name":"references","attrs":{"group":"note","responsive":"1"},"body":{"html":""}}'><ol class="mw-references references" data-mw-group="note"><li about="#cite_note-3" id="cite_note-3"><a href="./Leo_Tolstoy#cite_ref-3" data-mw-group="note" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-3" class="mw-reference-text">Tolstoy pronounced his first name as <small about="#mwt14" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"IPA-ru","href":"./Template:IPA-ru"},"params":{"1":{"wt":"lʲɵf"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAfc">Russian pronunciation:<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwAfg"> </span></small><span title="Representation in the International Phonetic Alphabet (IPA)" class="IPA" about="#mwt14" id="mwAfk"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./Help:IPA/Russian" title="Help:IPA/Russian" id="mwAfo">[lʲɵf]</a></span>, which corresponds to the Romanisation <i id="mwAfs">Lyov</i>. (<cite class="citation book" about="#mwt15" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite book ","href":"./Template:Cite_book"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Nabokov"},"first":{"wt":"Vladimir"},"title":{"wt":"Lectures on Russian literature"},"page":{"wt":"216"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwAfw">Nabokov, Vladimir. <i id="mwAf0">Lectures on Russian literature</i>. p.<span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwAf4"> </span>216.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Lectures+on+Russian+literature&amp;rft.pages=216&amp;rft.aulast=Nabokov&amp;rft.aufirst=Vladimir&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALeo+Tolstoy" class="Z3988" about="#mwt15" id="mwAf8"></span><style data-mw-deduplicate="TemplateStyles:r879151008" typeof="mw:Extension/templatestyles" about="#mwt15" data-mw='{"name":"templatestyles","attrs":{"src":"Module:Citation/CS1/styles.css"},"body":{"extsrc":""}}