66"><a href="./Leo_Tolstoy#cite_ref-66" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-66" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation journal" about="#mwt242" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"cite journal ","href":"./Template:Cite_journal"},"params":{"last":{"wt":"Wenzer"},"first":{"wt":"Kenneth C."},"year":{"wt":"1997"},"title":{"wt":"Tolstoy&apos;s Georgist Spiritual Political Economy (1897–1910): Anarchism and Land Reform"},"journal":{"wt":"[[The American Journal of Economics and Sociology]]"},"volume":{"wt":"56"},"issue":{"wt":"4, Oct"},"pages":{"wt":"639–667"},"jstor":{"wt":"3487337"}},"i":0}}]}' id="mwA1M">Wenzer, Kenneth C. (1997). "Tolstoy's Georgist Spiritual Political Economy (1897–1910): Anarchism and Land Reform". <i id="mwA1Q"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./The_American_Journal_of_Economics_and_Sociology" title="The American Journal of Economics and Sociology" id="mwA1U">The American Journal of Economics and Sociology</a></i>. <b id="mwA1Y">56</b> (4, Oct): 639–667. <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="./JSTOR" title="JSTOR" id="mwA1c">JSTOR</a><span typeof="mw:Entity" id="mwA1g"> </span><a rel="mw:ExtLink" class="external text" href="//www.jstor.org/stable/3487337" id="mwA1k">3487337</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+American+Journal+of+Economics+and+Sociology&amp;rft.atitle=Tolstoy%27s+Georgist+Spiritual+Political+Economy+%281897%E2%80%931910%29%3A+Anarchism+and+Land+Reform&amp;rft.volume=56&amp;rft.issue=4%2C+Oct&amp;rft.pages=639-667&amp;rft.date=1997&amp;rft_id=%2F%2Fwww.jstor.org%2Fstable%2F3487337&amp;rft.aulast=Wenzer&amp;rft.aufirst=Kenneth+C.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALeo+Tolstoy" class="Z3988" about="#mwt242" id="mwA1o"></span><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r879151008" about="#mwt242" typeof="m