stoy#cite_ref-83" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-83" class="mw-reference-text">Wallace, Irving, 'Everybody's Rover Boy', in <i id="mwA5s">The Sunday Gentleman</i>. New York: Simon &amp; Schuster, 1965. p. 117.</span></li></ol></div>

